name: PixelFlow v1.3.0 (62)
body:
```
PixelFlow v1.3.0 (62)

source
- updated Softbodydynamics: DwParticles, DwConstraints
- updated and improved HalfEdge structure, IFS
- new Utils: smoothstep, etc...

examples
- new 2D-Softbody examples: differential growth
- new examples in misc (e.g. mutliple windows + pixelflow context)
- updated bulletphyscis+HeMesh examples

fixes
- bugfix: collision-rid (head-pointer start value)
- bugfix: FlowFieldParticles display shader 
  (https://github.com/diwi/PixelFlow/issues/21)

```
